  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Introduction"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The modules developed in China Convergence Base should be designed and implemented in a way that it an be reused across multiple projects"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Repo Structure"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Platform repos"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "All the platform code has to be implemented in the respective repos which is placed in below path"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Autosar\\cnconvbase"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Example, For Audio modules"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Autosar\\cnconvbase\\audio"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Project repos"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "All the project configuration of respective platform modules should be implemented in Config repos placed in below path"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Config\\Autosar\\audio"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Guidelines for Platform modules"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Make sure platform repo code only has the core logic and all project specific implementation has to be implemented as callouts and Configuration files in Config repos"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "An example for State of Health module"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Aurix%20-%20China%20Convergence%20Platform%20Module%20Guidelines/image2022-7-5_15-15-27.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Aurix - China Convergence Platform Module Guidelines/image2022-7-5_15-15-27.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "All modules should have an done following tasks"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "Functional Test Spec",
        "Unit Test report (Google/CPPUnitTest)",
        "QAC/Coverity report",
        "Manual/Wiki for the project integration team"
      ]
    }
  ],
